query: SELECT p.id, s.name as service_name, c.name as country_name, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice FROM prices p JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id WHERE s.name IN ('whatsapp', 'google', 'telegram', 'Vk.com') ORDER BY s.name LIMIT 10
